---
title: Grilled Ribeye Steak with Miso Butter and Soy-Glazed Sweet Potatoes and Sesame Broccoli
description: This steak dinner, inspired by Japanese steakhouses, is loaded with tons of flavour. Miso butter tops grilled steak, while soy-brushed sweet potatoes and sesame broccoli round a perfect summer meal.

